description: An ultra-technical hiking shoe that helps you achieve all your outdoor goals. Designed to adapt to all your desires, the Outpulse Mid GORE-TEX is as versatile as it is efficient. Combining grip and protection, this model has a sole that offers exceptional energy return and cushioning thanks to our new Fuze Foam. Reinvent your outdoor adventures.
name: Salomon Outpulse Mid GTX - Mens
